## Example

When you are working with text (e.g., natural language) data:

``` r
## load wactor package
library(wactor)

## text data (sentences)
word <- function() {
  paste(sample(letters, sample(2:10, 1), replace = TRUE), collapse = "")
}
sentence <- function() {
  paste0(paste(replicate(sample(3:12, 1), word()), collapse = " "), ".")
}

## setence data pt 1
s1 <- replicate(50, sentence())

## setence data pt 2
```
